<p><img height="185" width="300" src="http://www.edenhrconsulting.com/images/stories/eden-stick-figures/eden-recruit.jpg" alt="eden-recruit" style="float: right;" />Sourcing and sifting high quality applicants can be difficult whatever the economic climate. Do you really know what to look for? Do you know what competencies your are expecting the candidates to display?</p>
<p>Eden HR Consulting can assist you in sourcing and sifting candidates in proven and reliable ways to aid your business.  This can be achieved through transposing your job description into a legally compliant job advertisement, searching CV job sites or headhunting.  We even have experience of instigating preferred supplier lists (PSL) where clients have use of industry specifc recruitment agencies, lowering the fees paid.</p>
<p>We work very differently from an agency, we do not have a database of candidates, however we can source candidates from various sources with great results.  We do not charge a fixed fee or pencentage of starting salary - we charge our time which is more often than not considerably cheaper than using a recruitment agency. As well as being more cost effective, we are HR qualified which makes us equipped to finding the right candidates for our clients.</p></td>
</tr>

